S.FORM: Dave Allen kawas tay 1958, Dave Allen, squliq na Bunge'. qyanux nya Allen htgan ru mrkyas beh Naperville, Illinois. hiya mason pqwasan biru maki Naperville, Central . maki qasa hiya "Groover" lalu nya. suruw lga, "Gruber" lalu nya. mincyogun nya hiya ga semon hmyapas squliq.
